GlobalTableDef.Name: SLT_Cases
GlobalTableDef.Description: Contains one entry for each Case in the database

GlobalTableDef.Name: SLT_CaseModelTables
GlobalTableDef.Description: One row for each user-system and user-default table

GlobalTableDef.Name: SLT_CaseModelFields
GlobalTableDef.Description: Contains one row for each field of every user-system and user-default table

GlobalTableDef.Name: SLT_TableDefs
GlobalTableDef.Description: Contains one row for each end-user-visible table in the system

View.ViewText: select T1.CaseID, T1.Name 'TableName', F1.* from dbo.SLT_FieldDefs F1, dbo.SLT_TableDefs T1 where F1.TableID = T1.TableID
View.Name: V_SLT_Fields
